Package org.wiredwidgets.cow.webapp.client.page

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Admin
    Page with special admin buttons Currently, the only admin control deletes all active workflows
    CreateNewTask
    Page that creates a new public task
    EditWorkflow
    Page to edit a workflow There are a lot of instanceof calls on this page, because there is currently no Interface linking Activity and Option.
    Login
    Simple login page; does not check any credentials, but the user name is used to get Tasks for that user.
    ManageWorkflows
    A page that lets users view all saved workflows and select one to view or edit.
    ManageWorkflows2
    A page that lets users view all saved workflows and select one to view or edit.
    PageWidget
    Base class for all pages.
    Tasks
    Home page that lets users see all their assigned tasks to complete, assign public tasks to themself, or view tasks they've recently completed.
    ViewActiveWorkflows  
    ViewWorkflow
    Page to view a workflow, without being able to edit it
